un for the 800m by 101 women for whom data was available at both ages 12 (horizontal axis) and at age 19; the red line indicates the qualifying time for the 2023 European U20 Championship 800m.\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The graph\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"the times\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"101 women\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"both ages\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"12 (horizontal axis\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"the red line\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying time\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 European U20 Championship\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"800m.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the bottom left you see the teen sensations, thosae athletes who had always performed at the top of their age group.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"the teen sensations\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \", thosae athletes\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"their age group\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But notice also that many of the athletes who would go on to achieve the qualifying time for major championships were not amongst the top athletes at age 12.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying time\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"major championships\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"the top athletes\", \"from\"